Airway stent: what is new and what should be discarded.

Herth FJ(1), Eberhardt R.

Author information:
(1)Department of Pneumology and Critical Care Medicine, Thoraxklinik, 
Translational Lung Research Center Heidelberg, German Center for Lung Research 
